16 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Transition. Notwithstanding the provisions of [section 6], the department
17 of public health and human services shall settle all cost reports submitted prior to [the effective date of this act]
18 within 240 days of [the effective date of this act].
19
20 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Appropriation. (1) There is appropriated $33,900 from the general fund
21 and $33,900 from the federal special revenue fund to the department of public health and human services for
22 the fiscal year beginning July 1, 2025, for the settlement of cost reports described in [sections 3 and 4].
23 (2) There is appropriated $7,500 from the general fund and $7,500 from the federal special
